                    </div>
                    <span>I heard Keith Harrell speak at a sales meeting in January and immediately bought his book. Keith is the real deal. He weaves stories about his life into the principles he reveals about how much our attitude effects our lives and the lives of those around us. He obviously has a relationship with God, and he uses that relationship as the foundation stone for his belief system. I highly recommend this book for adults and teenagers alike.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Amazing Book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
