                    <span>Attitude Is Everything<P>After reading this book if you don't come away with changes you need to make in your life or the way you react to situations then you have missed the whole point of the book. This book will leave you energized and with a new passion for life. <P>In "Attitude is Everything", Keith Harrell will give you 10 steps to show everyone how to take control of their attitude and in doing so their life, which will allow them to reach their full potential. We, alone, have the ability to transform life and reach for everything we want both personally and professionally and all we need is one tool...Our Attitude</span>
                  
              
